  "title": "Boring Job not for you? READ THIS 📌",
  "description": "<p><br />🛠️<strong> What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>🗣️ Talk to people, tell stories & make brands pop IRL</p><p>🎪 Rep big-name clients at outdoor events & activations</p><p>🎤 Level up your communication & confidence (fast)</p><p>🤝 Run with a high-energy team that actually moves</p><p>🧠<strong> What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>🤚🏼 Real mentorship (not “figure it out yourself”)</p><p>💸 Performance-based rewards, bonuses & recognition</p><p>✈️ Regional exposure + clear growth paths</p><p>🏆 A team that wins together & celebrates loud</p><p>👀<strong> We’re Looking For You If You…</strong></p><p>☀️ Love being outdoors & meeting new people</p><p>⚡ Learn fast, adapt fast, move fast</p><p>🥊 Aren’t scared of mistakes — you see challenges as upgrades</p><p>🔥 Are 18–25, hungry, driven & want <strong>more</strong> than “just a job”</p><p>🙉 No experience? Chill. Training’s on us.</p><p>🫡<strong> </strong>Why us</p><p>This isn’t a desk job.</p><p>It’s for people who want growth, confidence, income & experiences.</p><p>You bring the hustle — we bring the platform.</p><p>Every day = a chance to level up.</p>",
